===Awards and memberships=== Antoine received the French [[Legion of Honor]] on 27 September 1850 with the order of chevalier or knight.<ref name="ww" /> He was a member of the [[Bureau des Longitudes]] and also the [[French Academy of Sciences]].<ref name="ww" /> Both brothers received the grand medal of the [[Paris Geographical Society]]<ref name="ww" /> in 1850.
